column2: SELECT   z.allamID,z.ra1,z.dec1,z.ra2,z.dec2,z.allam_redshift1,z.allam_redshift2,z.ra as ra_dr7,z.dec as dec_dr7,   z.SpecObjID as SpecObjID_dr7,z.mjd as mjd_dr7,z.plate as plate_dr7,z.fiberID as fiberID_dr7,z.z as z_dr7,   p.objID as objID_dr1#,p.ra as ra_ra1#,p.dec as dec_dr1#,p.SpecObjID as SpecObjID_dr1#_p,   s.bestObjID as bestObjID_dr1#,s.SpecObjID as SpecObjID_dr1#_s,s.mjd as mjd_dr1#,s.plate as plate_dr1#,s.fiberID as fiberID_dr1#,s.z as z_dr1# into mydb.test FROM dr1#.PhotoObjAll as p   JOIN dr1#.SpecObjAll as s ON s.specObjID=p.specObjID   JOIN mydb.zlost as z ON z.mjd=s.mjd WHERE   s.plate=z.plate   AND s.fiberID=z.fiberID ORDER BY   z.allamID
